272	6. How to Use (Planned Flow)
273	# First time
274	gha-isolated init
275	
276	# Start runners
277	gha-isolated start
278	
279	# Check status
280	gha-isolated status
281	
282	# Install as service (future)
283	gha-isolated install-service
284	On GCE: Create a Linux VM → cargo install gha-isolated (or copy binary) → run the same commands.
